      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703294,
      "updated": 1777703347
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5997e0000000000ae702a",
      "text": " \t\tcode:ページ名「だいこん」",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703294,
      "updated": 1777703347
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5997e0000000000ae702b",
      "text": " \t\t だいこん",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703294,
      "updated": 1777703347
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5997e0000000000ae702c",
      "text": " \t\t \t[野菜]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703294,
      "updated": 1777703347
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5997e0000000000ae702d",
      "text": " \t\tcode:ページ名「にんじん」",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703294,
      "updated": 1777703347
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5997e0000000000ae702e",
      "text": " \t\t にんじん",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703294,
      "updated": 1777703347
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5997e0000000000ae702f",
      "text": " \t\t \t[野菜]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703294,
      "updated": 1777703347
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5997e0000000000ae7030",
      "text": " \t\tcode:ページ名「ごぼう」",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703294,
      "updated": 1777703347
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5997e0000000000ae7031",
      "text": " \t\t ごぼう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703294,
      "updated": 1777703347
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5997e0000000000ae7032",
      "text": " \t\t \t[野菜]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703294,
      "updated": 1777703347
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5997e0000000000ae7033",
      "text": " \t\tcode:ページ名「はくさい」",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703294,
      "updated": 1777703347
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5997e0000000000ae7034",
      "text": " \t\t はくさい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703294,
      "updated": 1777703347
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5997e0000000000ae7035",
      "text": " \t\t \t[野菜]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703294,
      "updated": 1777703347
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5997e0000000000ae7036",
      "text": " \t\tcode:ページ名「トマト」",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703294,
      "updated": 1777703347
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5997e0000000000ae7037",
      "text": " \t\t トマト",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703294,
      "updated": 1777703347
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5997e0000000000ae7038",
      "text": " \t\t \t[野菜]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703294,
      "updated": 1777703347
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5997e0000000000ae7039",
      "text": " \t\tcode:ページ名「キャベツ」",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703294,
      "updated": 1777703347
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5997e0000000000ae703a",
      "text": " \t\t キャベツ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703294,
      "updated": 1777703347
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5997e0000000000ae703b",
      "text": " \t\t \t[やさい]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703294,
      "updated": 1777703347
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5997e0000000000ae703c",
      "text": "\t多分個々のページに書く内容がそれほどない場合は（先の例で言えば「記念」のページに収集するように）どこか最も象徴的なページに集積するのが良いかも。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703294,
      "updated": 1777703347
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5997e0000000000ae703d",
      "text": "\t\tなお、この方法を取ると[大きすぎるリンクの問題]が生じる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703294,
      "updated": 1777703347
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5997e0000000000ae703e",
      "text": "\t\tあー。別個のページが欲しくなってしまう[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703294,
      "updated": 1777703347
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5997e0000000000ae703f",
      "text": "\t\t\t生理的にそうなるだけ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703294,
      "updated": 1777703347
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5997e0000000000ae7040",
      "text": "\t\t\tカードのメタファではないがひとつの実体としてそれぞれに1ページ欲しいんだろう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703294,
      "updated": 1777703347
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5997e0000000000ae7041",
      "text": "\t\tおもろい[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777703294,
      "updated": 1777703347
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5997e0000000000ae7042",
